{"tid":1509293,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［電腦硬件白痴］MBP 17 vs 19","createTime":"2019-08-26T19:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T20:51:34.000Z","uid":276851,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bdae3eebd64a8b8b963476081e31f65543f02257","tid":1509293,"uid":276851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:32:29.000Z","msg":"小弟得部垃圾家用文書機，<br />\n想換部MBP&hellip;<br />\n但平時用電腦都係用Google 雲端堆文書野、YouTube 、睇波、聽歌、執下相、同cut下片（imovie)&hellip;<br />\n知摟屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但全屋人都係用蘋果野&hellip;想一體化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到apple 翻新機 17年 MBP 16GB ram 都係9399<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ovETbqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FovETbqf.png&h=ac92e0e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cstdbqg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCstdbqg.png&h=3d608bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但19年 8GB ram 都係貴一千左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HGaX5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HGaX5n.png&h=3e7d32f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網見跑分 19年 四核 <span style=\"color: red;\">屌打</span> 17年雙核<br />\n<br />\n但又唔知兩代 8GB ram 同16GB ram 有咩分別<br />\n用上嚟速度會唔會差好遠？<br />\n<br />\n定價又近 搞到唔知買邊部好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3627020f601ca892a35713c1e91b826f3d05f2","tid":1509293,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQr